name: BANNER LOGO T-SHIRT - CHARCOAL | Was $24.99
description:
Like I said before the Banner Collage graphic and design has been growing within the fans but my dear friend Paris asked me one day, have I ever done just a plain Banner Logo shirt? Then I realized I never have!
How have I never made a shirt with our staple design?!
Thanks for the inspiration Paris, this on is for you!

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the top back.
Available in Charcoal and Burgundy.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: BANNER COLLAGE T-SHIRT | Was $24.99
description:
The ever so growing Banner Collage is back again this season with a colorful spring twist. This graphic has evolved into another staple design within the company and fans always ask for it.
These are probably my favorite colorways we've done so far!

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the top back.
Available in Charcoal Heather and Black.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: BOLLA KILLS T-SHIRT | Was $24.99
description:
The slogan that killed it, pun intended.
My life motto is Carpe Diem. Pretty much put in everything you got or nothing, go hard or go home. Kill at everything I do. 

Back in my writing years, I used to write "Bolla Will Kill One Day." Stating that I will kill it with Bolla. I'm going to put everything I got into this and push to the limit. Slowly it became the company slogan and everyone just caught on it.
Short, simple, and straight to the point. The perfect marketing design I could ever ask for. 

My company is not called Bolla Kills but it came to the point where it just evolved into it. Call it what you want, its all the same!

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the top back.
Available in Burgundy and Black.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: BODIES T-SHIRT - ROYAL | Was $24.99
description:
The infamous bodies graphic! It has been one of our signature designs online and on our stickers. Finally now available in a wearable medium!
This shirt has been another one of our sleeper hits and the response has been great. But then there those jackasses who give me shit, whatever!
This is art at its most natural form, appreciate it!!!

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the top back.
Available in Charcoal and Royal.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: BOL"LA" T-SHIRT | Was $24.99
description:
Back by popular demand, our rendition on the Los Angeles graphic. I been getting asked constantly to bring this graphic back but like all my designs, once it's sold out, it's sold out.

The only way I bring back the design is if something is changed. Unfortunately the back graphic that was on the original version is no longer there. Like I said, you snooze, you loose. This is the closest you'll get it.

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the top back.
Available in Denim Heather and Black.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: DOS T-SHIRT | Was $24.99
description:
The Dos graphic is a continuation of last year's anniversary graphic. Everyone loved the Old School culture style show girl I drew so I brought it back for the second year anniversary, this time bigger!
Uno is one, Dos is two... get it?!

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the back.
Available in White and Athletic Heather.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: DREAMER T-SHIRT | Was $24.99
description:
The Dreamer series has been turning into a sleepers hit. The industry has been running Native American or tribal inspired graphics a lot this past year. I think it's because a lot of us can find some sort of relation to the culture.

My interpretation and rendition of this graphics has a lot of meaning behind it. It touches the basis of feminism, dreams, wishful thinking, action taking, and Americana.

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Large graphic printed on the back.
Available in White and Red.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: KILLERS T-SHIRT | Was $24.99
description:
This seasons colorways are heavily inspired by sports and their corresponding city colors. It was only right to create a sport inspired graphic to go along with it.
Introducing our team's name... The Bolla Killers!
This our rendition on the famous Oakland Raider's throwback graphic with a Bolla twist.

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the top back.
Available in Royal and Black.

name: TWENTY THREE T-SHIRT | Was $24.99
description:
Sneaker culture has always been a huge part of my life. I started pretty early with collecting, though it is nothing compare to what others have... trust me.
It all started with skate shoes, then ventured off to lifestyle, running, high-end, and now I'm working with Nike. It's amazing how one thing just leads to the next as long as you're consistent.

This graphic is inspired by one the all time greatest and the legend of all sneakers!

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small bubble logo printed on the top back.
Available in Red and Athletic Heather.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: BUBBLE CROWN (BOLLA. + ROYAL/T) T-SHIRT - BLACK | Was $24.99
description:
This collaboration is very close to my heart. I've done many big name projects with other companies and organizations but this is one of my top 3.

The 2-year anniversary party itself was super insane but to get an opportunity to have a pop-up shop and collaborate with this organization was a huge stepping stone with my company and the fine arts and design world. Just networking and showcasing my brand, it was truly a surreal experience.

When it came time to do a collaborative piece to sell, doing a shirt was a no brainer and just combining our two logos fit just like a glove. It was all meant to be. This was also the very first time I ever changed the bubble logo to any other color than our signature colorways.
It was originally sold exclusively at Royal/T but we had a few left and I managed to put it up online for those who couldn't make it to the event or pop-up shop. Own a piece of this history!

100% pre-shrunk cotton t-shirt.
Large graphic screen printed on the front. Small Bolla. + Royal/T graphic printed on the top back.
Available in White and Black.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: BANNER COLLAGE IPHONE 4/4S CASE - CHERRY
description:
Smartphones have pretty much became an extension and necessity to our everyday lives. We feel naked without it and for something that we care about so much should also be taken care of.

For our first iPhone case we teamed up with our good friend over at Goodwood NYC for our completely custom case.
iPhone cases have become so saturated in the accessory industry. They're either extremely high-tech or designed very poorly.
So when it came time to make ours, we made sure to go to the experts and came up with something everyone can enjoy!

- iPhone 4/4s 
- Rubberized Soft-touch framing/interior for extra grip/security
- Ultra slim snap-on design
- Custom engraved wood design on the exterior
- Easy access to all features/ports
- Made in U.S.A.

*Color/darkness may vary due to the natural state of the wood condition. No two are alike.

name: SPECKLE SOCKS - BLACK
description:
The sock game is insane right. To be honest I used to care less about what I put on my feet. I just thought socks were socks, nothing special until the industry really started making high quality socks.
Once I slipped on a pair, I was instantly hooked and there was no going back.

Here is our take on high quality socks. We are really excited about these.
Custom designed from color ways, thread count, size, fit, all the way down to the packaging. It was long process but we are backing these bad boys 110%.
Once you slip on a pair, you too will never go back to those 3pack department store socks.
So grab a pair, grab 10 actually. You'll thank us later.

- High quality, speckle design.
- Bolla Kills logo on both sides.
- One size fits all.
- Available in Black and Orange.

name: BANNER COLLAGE DECK - BLACK
description:
I am very very happy to introduce you to our full line of skateboard decks.

As all of you know by now, skateboard culture is the backbone of this company, without it nothing would exist. It is a huge part of my life. 
It introduced me to the art worlds, gave me my courage and motivation to push, gave me my first job, and the list goes on and on.
Once I had the opportunity to start making my own, I couldn't resist.

Skateboarding has grew into such a huge industry and hitting so many different genres of styles, the opportunities are endless. Not only is this wooden toy creating professional sport careers but its also giving back to the community and artists as well.
Skate decks have become a sought after collector items where high-end companies are using decks as canvas pieces which allows affordable hanging art, it is crazy!

This is my way of giving back to the culture while still sticking to the roots and showing the high-end exclusivity of limited art decks.

The deck are available in an array of sizes from cruisers to street decks.
Cold-pressed water based construction:
-Light weight
-Medium durability
-Polished finish
-Comparable to Girl/Chocolate boards

Bolla Skateboard Co.
Made in Los Angeles.

name: BUBBLE LOGO ANNIVERSARY KEYCHAIN - COPPER
description:
2012 marks our 2-year anniversary for the company and I wanted to make something special to commemorate this occasion.
I decided to custom-make our world famous bubble logo and custom mold it into a keychain so you can hang it anywhere!

The bubble logo is very close to my heart. It has gotten me to places I could never imagine, and I used this logo to also give back to others.
The reason I chose 100% copper was not just cause it fit the rustic style of the company but also because we're in a tough economical time right now.

Copper is worth more than gold and silver. I get pissed when people throw they're pennies away... who throws away money?!
If you save up all those and burn it, you have 100% copper that's worth more than that quarter of yours!
So with the anniversary keychain, if anything god forbids happens to you, know that, that bubble keychain always gots your back.
